<p>A Bad example, which reuses name <code class="highlighter-rouge">y</code>‚Ä¶</p>

<div class="language-coq highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><table class="rouge-table"><tbody><tr><td class="rouge-gutter gl"><pre class="lineno">1
</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre><span class="kp">intros</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="no">x</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="no">y</span><span class="pi">.</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kp">destruct</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="no">y</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="kr">as</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="o">[|</span><span class="no">y</span><span class="o">]</span><span class="w"> </span><span class="no">eqn</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="no">E</span><span class="pi">.</span><span class="w">
