<h2 id="qed"><code class="highlighter-rouge">Qed</code></h2>

<p>standing for Latin words <em>‚ÄúQuod Erat Demonstrandum‚Äù</em>‚Ä¶
meaning ‚Äúthat which was to be demonstrated‚Äù</p>
:ET